text: Hans Olof Holmström (15 October 1784, Ösmno Parish, Sweden - 27 August 1855 in Uppsala, Sweden) was a Swedish bishop. He was active within the Church of Sweden.. He was the Archbishop of Uppsala between 1852-1855. == References == Category:1784 births Category:1855 deaths Category:Swedish clergy Category:Archbishops of Uppsala
title: Hans Olof Holmström
